Package polyglot.util

Class SubtypeSet

java.lang.Object
polyglot.util.SubtypeSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<Type>, java.util.Collection<Type>, java.util.Set<Type>
public class SubtypeSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Set<Type>
Class to implement sets containing polyglot.types.Type. Set membership is based on the subtype relationships. Thus, if S is a supertype of A and B, then { S } union { A, B } = { S }. Similarly, we remove elements from the set such that if s is an element of a set S, then a call to remove r removes all s s.t. r is a a supertype of s.
